Invocation Name: priority board
des: Priority Board helps you get things done. Research shows that focusing on one task at a time is the best way to get things done. Priority board only lets you add a few items to your task list and if you're not done by the end of the day, your tasks reset. In this way, you'll have to ask yourself "Am I working on the most important task, right now?". Complete your tasks and tell Priority Board you're done.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
